ense!\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented the dedicated coverage test:\n\n- Added `tests/src/org.springframework/spring-core/5.3.15/src/test/java/org_springframework/spring_core/MixinEverythingEmitterTest.java`\n\nThe new test exercises `Mixin.Generator` with `Mixin.STYLE_EVERYTHING`, which routes through `MixinEverythingEmitter` and reaches the remaining uncovered `Class#getMethods()` dynamic-access call site. It also follows the Native Image dynamic class-loading error handling pattern already used by nearby CGLIB tests.\n\nPer your instruction, I did not compile or run the tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0567e18e41df493c0169f5b043e76481a0bbbf542ff4521e2e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 775, "output": 636, "cacheRead": 26624, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 28035, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777709112506, "responseId": "resp_0567e18e41df493c0169f5b03908c081a08667ea3d51d4d8c8"}, "toolResults": []}
